  "body": "Starting on this release, we'll stop updating the CHANGELOG.md and use the GitHub releases page instead.\r\n\r\n## Highlighted changes:\r\n* security improvements by @curious-rabbit in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/951\r\n* fix exit code in non-interactive mode by @valoq in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1011\r\n* fix: ignore invalid unix permissions and setuid bits from zip by @tommady in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1007\r\n\r\n## Other Changes\r\n* tweak extract logic in preparation for sandboxing @valoq in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/996\r\n* ci: bump actions/checkout from 6 to 6.0.2 in the github-actions group by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1002\r\n* ci: bump actions/checkout from 6.0.2 to 6.0.3 in the github-actions group by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1009\r\n* deps: bump tar from 0.4.45 to 0.4.46 in the cargo-patch-and-minor group by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/997\r\n* deps: bump the cargo-patch-and-minor group with 11 updates by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1003, https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1010 and https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/pull/1013\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch/compare/0.8.0...0.8.1",
